ary cap.\n\n==== Team Performance ====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n!Team\n!Winners\n!Runners-up\n!Years won\n!Years runner-up\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|South Sydney|16}} [[South Sydney Rabbitohs]]\n|21\n|13\n|1908, 1909, 1914, 1918, 1925, 1926, 1927, 1928, 1929, 1931,\n1932, 1950, 1951, 1953, 1954, 1955, 1967, 1968, 1970, 1971,\n\n2014\n|1910, 1916, 1917, 1920, 1923, 1924, 1935, 1937, 1939, 1949,\n1952, 1965, 1969\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|Eastern Suburbs|16}} [[Sydney Roosters]]\n|15\n|15\n|1911, 1912, 1913, 1923, 1935, 1936, 1937, 1940, 1945, 1974,\n1975, 2002, 2013, 2018, 2019\n|1908, 1919, 1921, 1928, 1931, 1934, 1938, 1941, 1960, 1972,\n1980, 2000, 2003, 2004, 2010\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|St. George|16}} [[St. George Dragons|St George Dragons]]\n|15\n|12\n|1941, 1949, 1956, 1957, 1958, 1959, 1960, 1961, 1962, 1963,\n1964, 1965, 1966, 1977, 1979\n|1927, 1930, 1933, 1942, 1946, 1953, 1971, 1975, 1985, 1992,\n1993, 1996\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|Balmain|16}} [[Balmain Tigers]]\n|11\n|9\n|1915, 1916, 1917, 1919, 1920, 1924, 1939, 1944, 1946, 1947,\n1969\n|1909, 1936, 1945, 1948, 1956, 1964, 1966, 1988, 1989\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|Manly|16}} [[Manly-Warringah Sea Eagles]]\n|8\n|11\n|1972, 1973, 1976, 1978, 1987, 1996, 2008, 2011\n|1951, 1957, 1959, 1968, 1970, 1982, 1983, 1995, 1997, 2007,\n2013\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|Canterbury|16}} [[Canterbury-Bankstown Bulldogs]]\n|8\n|10\n|1938, 1942, 1980, 1984, 1985, 1988, 1995, 2004\n|1940, 1947, 1967, 1974, 1979, 1986, 1994, 1998, 2012, 2014\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|Brisbane|16}} [[Brisbane Broncos]]\n|6\n|1\n|1992, 1993, 1997, 1998, 2000, 2006\n|2015\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|Western Suburbs|16}} [[Western Suburbs Magpies]]\n|4\n|8\n|1930, 1934, 1948, 1952\n|1918, 1925, 1932, 1950, 1958, 1961, 1962, 1963\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|Parramatta|16}} [[Parramatta Eels]]\n|4\n|5\n|1981, 1982, 1983, 1986\n|1976, 1977, 1984, 2001, 2009\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|Newtown|16}} [[Newtown Jets]]\n|3\n|7\n|1910, 1933, 1943\n|1913, 1914, 1929, 1944, 1954, 1955, 1981\n|-\n|{{leagueicon|Melbou